### Test request

@hostname = httpbin.org

GET /anything HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Host: https://{{hostname}}


### POST json

POST https://httpbin.org/anything HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
User-Agent: kulala.nvim/5.3.4 HTTP/1.1

{
  "details": {
    "type": "example",
    "value": 100
  },
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Test Item",
  "tags": [
    "testing",
    "json"
  ],
  "valid": true
}


### POST json file

POST https://httpbin.org/anything HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
User-Agent: kulala.nvim/5.3.4 HTTP/1.1

< ./test.uat.json
